# Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA)

- Contrast: Normal text must meet 4.5:1; large text 3:1.
- Keyboard: All interactive elements must be reachable with Tab.
  Visible focus indicators must be present. If outline is removed,
  replace with: :focus-visible { outline: 3px solid #9edd05; outline-offset: 2px; }
- Images: Informative images need descriptive alt text.
  Decorative images use alt="".
- Forms: Every input must have a label. Placeholder text cannot be
  the only label. Error messages must be announced with role="alert".
- Motion: Respect prefers-reduced-motion.
- Touch targets: Must be at least 44px x 44px.
